ABOUT THE PROJECT:
DevNovate is a comprehensive full-stack blog platform built using the MERN stack
(MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) designed to provide a modern, feature-rich
blogging experience for developers and technology enthusiasts.

Key Features:
- User authentication and authorization
- Rich blog creation and editing interface
- Content management and moderation system
- Admin dashboard with analytics
- Responsive design with modern UI/UX
- Real-time feedback and interaction features
- User feedback collection system

